column5: Got out on the lake for some Day time Salmon      Caught a couple more before the phone died.
Way to go Greg, glad you got into them. Were you out yesterday off Grimsby? Because because I saw a few guys way out deeper. I was thinking of going out but we tried to stay on the Browns.
just off of Jordan and Fifty.  thanks Dave
nice going. Man I gotta get out there.
Nice job Greg    Couple of beauties
Those fish are tiny, I'll take you out to catch the big ones....if you don't sleep in.   Mark
